"<div><netz-page-heading caption="TP5 (2021-2022)"><span class="govuk-caption-l">TP5 (2021-2022)</span><!--container--><h1 class="govuk-heading-l">Baseline and targets</h1></netz-page-heading><!--container--><cca-highlight-diff><div class="govuk-!-display-none"><cca-summary><!--container--><dl govuk-summary-list="" class="govuk-summary-list govuk-!-margin-bottom-9"><div govuksummarylistrow="" class="govuk-summary-list__row"><dt govuksummarylistrowkey="" class="govuk-summary-list__key">Are you providing baseline and target information for TP5 (2021 to 2022)?</dt><dd govuksummarylistrowvalue="" class="govuk-summary-list__value"><!--container--><!--container--><!--container--><span>Yes</span><!--container--><!--container--><!--container--><!--container--></dd><dd govuksummarylistrowactions="" class="govuk-summary-list__actions"><a class="govuk-link" href="/?change=true">Change</a></dd><!--container--><!--container--></div><!--container--><!--container--><!--container--></dl><!--container--><h2 class="govuk-heading-m">Target composition</h2><!--container--><dl govuk-summary-list="" class="govuk-summary-list govuk-!-margin-bottom-9"><div govuksummarylistrow="" class="govuk-summary-list__row"><dt govuksummarylistrowkey="" class="govuk-summary-list__key">Target calculator file</dt><dd govuksummarylistrowvalue="" class="govuk-summary-list__value"><span>No files provided</span><!--container--><!--container--><!--container--><!--container--><!--container--></dd><dd govuksummarylistrowactions="" class="govuk-summary-list__actions"><a class="govuk-link" href="/?change=true">Change</a></dd><!--container--><!--container--></div><div govuksummarylistrow="" class="govuk-summary-list__row"><dt govuksummarylistrowkey="" class="govuk-summary-list__key">Energy or carbon units used by the sector</dt><dd govuksummarylistrowvalue="" class="govuk-summary-list__value"><!--container--><!--container--><!--container--><span>Energy (kWh)</span><!--container--><!--container--><!--container--><!-